      "text": [
        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : «مَنْ صَنَعَ إِلَى أَحَدٍ مِنْ أَهْلِ بَيْتِي يَداً كَافَيْتُهُ يَوْمَ اَلْقِيَامَةِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1725 - The Messenger of Allah (swt), peace be upon him and his family, said:\n\"Whoever extends a favor to any of my household, I will repay them on the Day of Judgment.\""
        ]
      }
